data.text: @VGKWarMachine Sad day when you present your best and get treated live a second class slave bay someone who you don't know in your own place.  Especially when you don't have the friends you need against someone who is constantly making your situation worst when I got no one
@DariaDarling @vicky_brogan @VGKWarMachine My husband drank like 9 of them 😂 BUT he had no issues except for a sore arm and a milk headache.
@BAMFbunny @vicky_brogan @VGKWarMachine Oh cool I'll pick some up when I get my shot. Imma do everything I can 🤣
@vicky_brogan @DariaDarling @VGKWarMachine I swear pedialyte is a miracle worker.
@vicky_brogan @AikmanCMU @VGKWarMachine I went with left, I figure I'm right handed and would prefer less pain there and just focus on moving my left arm
@vicky_brogan @VGKWarMachine @DariaDarling I used my right arm both times because I have a bad right shoulder so I’m already used to it being sore lol
@AikmanCMU @VGKWarMachine @vicky_brogan My arm was barely sore with the first one. This whole sleep thing you guys are talking about... I don't know how to do that 🤣🤣

@AikmanCMU @VGKWarMachine @DariaDarling I got the first shot in my left arm ('cause I'm a leftie) and the second shot in my right arm because I was told to move it around a lot...and I drive a stick shift Jeep. I figured that would help. It didn't. But...points to me for trying??? 😆
@DariaDarling @vicky_brogan @VGKWarMachine My dad didn’t any side effects either, unless he’s just being a stubborn old man and not admitting anything lol

@VGKWarMachine @vicky_brogan @DariaDarling First time I didn’t feel anything but I think I was more sore from exercising that arm after the second one and playing with my dogs to make sure the arm was loose and I think I overdid it lol
@AikmanCMU @vicky_brogan @VGKWarMachine Definitely hydrating and taking vitamins. I babysit a 3 year old all day, so I'm really hoping I'm as lucky as my mom and have no side effects at all

@AikmanCMU @vicky_brogan @DariaDarling Both times I was sore in the arm that they gave me the shot in.  Felt like someone kept punching my arm in the same place over and over.  In addition, I was just tired/exhausted.  Sleep was the cure.  Drink a lot of H2O. Mrs. didn’t have any of that.

@vicky_brogan @DariaDarling @VGKWarMachine Yup, all of that, I woke up the next just fine but as the day went on my temp went up(not bad) but it felt like a really bad migraine. 

For me sleep was the best and I always drink a ton of water anyway. The second day was much better but still a bit sore.
@DariaDarling @VGKWarMachine Rest, hydrate, Tylenol. Tomorrow may be yucky, but by Friday you should be good to go. Congratulations!
@DariaDarling I’m still careful, but it’s just reassuring knowing that The chance of catching the ‘rona is, “reduced.”  Risk mitigation is the key!
@VGKWarMachine I'm going to the game on Saturday so gotta be extra extra careful
@DariaDarling Once you get past that 2 weeks.... https://t.co/S9BZXqseRy
